  "slug": "fresh-norwegian-shrimp-skewers",
  "title": "Norwegian Shrimp Skewers",
  "description": "A simple and flavorful dish featuring succulent shrimp from Norway, marinated in a mix of Asian-inspired flavors. Perfect for a quick and easy dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Scandinavian",
